parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Unavailable Air Bag Recall Repair Parts
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unavailability of air bag recall repair parts poses a significant risk to vehicle occupants, as faulty air bags can lead to serious injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: None reported
as the issue is related to the unavailability of recall repair parts
not a specific failure or malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The inaccurate fuel gauge reading can cause the vehicle to run out of fuel and stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The fuel warning light illuminates when the gauge needle says there is still plenty of fuel left
differing amounts of fuel remaining
and the vehicle stalling while on the road.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The electrical shorts and problems can cause the vehicle to stall, lose power, and experience reduced engine performance, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Check engine light comes on and off
vehicle randomly fails to start
power lock/unlock key fob doesn't work
windows and sunroof power windows do not work
radio and dash turn off and restart
and check airbag light comes on and off.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The power train issues can cause the vehicle to lose power, experience reduced engine performance, and jerk or shake while shifting gears, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Transmission shifts with a loud thump
vehicle starts shaking and jerking while shifting gears
vehicle slows down
power reduces
and steering becomes difficult.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The airbag system malfunction can cause the airbags to not deploy in the event of an accident, leading to serious injury or death.
symptoms: Airbag warning light stays on
passenger airbag indicator light stays on
and airbag sensor malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The water leaks can cause electrical shorts, corrosion, and damage to the vehicle's systems, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.

sunroof
and windows

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The blind spot detection system malfunction can cause the system to not detect vehicles in the blind spot, leading to accidents.
